dmca.title: German complains of racist sites in Google.de search
dmca.body:
We received the email below on July 11, 2005. These sites are
allegedly illegal under German law. We have removed these sites from
www.google.de.

Date: Mon, Jul 11 2005 8:59 am  
Subject: abuse - fascist websites  

please delete the following fascist, rascist websites from your 
directory: 

http://www.thepaganfront.com 
http://www.stormfront.org 
http://www.nsbm.org 
http://www.ultima.fr.pl/ 

thanks in advance!
